                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170521-79-off397 t18170521-79-cd398"></join>, at <placeName id="t18170521-79-crimeloc399">St. Luke's</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18170521-79-crimeloc399" type="placeName" value="St. Luke's"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170521-79-crimeloc399" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170521-79-off397 t18170521-79-crimeloc399"></join>, two hearth-rugs, value 14s.; seven blankets, value 20s.; three pillows, value 10s.; one bolster, value 5s.; one shirt, value 5s.; three shifts, value 10s.; and one pair of shoes, value 4s.; the property of 
                     <persName id="t18170521-79-victim546" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
                        Locke
                     <interp inst="t18170521-79-victim546" type="surname" value="Locke"></interp>
